(1121, 409, '_field_90', 'Youths behavior improved dramatically this week. He seemed to be adjusting to his afterschool schedule and did a much better job following directions. ISS worker continued training youth on hygiene, school work and ADL skills.\n\nYouth did well as far as following directions while bathing and brushing his teeth, however it was more difficult for him to follow instructions when it came to washing dishes and tying his shoes. He would stop doing what he was doing and begin asking for his iPad. ISS worker had to remind youth several times of the time he received his iPad and this seemed to frustrate youth a lot. Youth did less throwing on the floor and more of expressing himself.'),
