(1375, 430, '_field_82', ' I do not about any mediation'),
(1376, 430, '_field_83', 'For this week the IST is going to work on her personal hygiene and cleansing. We\'re going to work with her temper problems and listening to her family at communicating with others. And to keep doing your homework..'),
