used intervention style. Experience utilizing positive behavior supports is a plus.\r\n\r\n<strong>Required Skills </strong>\r\n-Minimum of master\'s degree in related field\r\n-Current valid New Jersey clinical license (LAC/LPC, LMFTA/LMFT, and LSW/LCSW or Licensed Psychologist)\r\n-Valid NJ Driver\'s License and ability to travel to clients\' homes\r\n\r\n<strong>Required Experience </strong>\r\n1+ years of experience working with children with mental health and behavioral challenges.\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:18:\"Licensed Clinician\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:18:\"licensed-clinician\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2017-10-11 18:24:25\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-10-11 18:24:25\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:54:\"http://newcarenj.org/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=338\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:336;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2017-09-18 14:57:25\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-09-18 14:57:25\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:936:\"<div class=\"page-margin\" style=\"margin: 5%; font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n<h2>Board Certified Behavior Analyst (BCBA)</h2>\r\n<p><b>Job Type:</b> Part-Time / Per Diem</p><br>\r\n<strong>Job Description</strong><br>\r\n-Conduct functional behavioral assessments<br>\r\n-Create programs and behavior intervention plans<br>\r\n-Complete skill assessments, including ABLLS-R, VB-MAPP and AFLS<br>\r\n-Train and supervise school staff and/or home therapists<br>\r\n-Parent training<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong> Required Skills</strong><br>\r\n-Masters Degree in Psychology, Special Education or related field.<br>\r\n-Current BCBA certification.<br>\r\n-Access to reliable transportation; willingness to travel.<br>\r\n-Strong interpersonal and writing skills.<br>\r\n-Ability to work well with others and be an effective part of a treatment team.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Required Experience</strong>\r\n2+ years of experience working with children on the autism spectrum.\r\n\r\n</div>\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:39:\"Board Certified Behavior Analyst (BCBA)\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:37:\"board-certified-behavior-analyst-bcba\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2017-10-11 18:24:55\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-10-11 18:24:55\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:54:\"http://newcarenj.org/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=336\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:2;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:333;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2017-09-18 14:52:26\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-09-18 14:52:26\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:1141:\"<div class=\"page-margin\" style=\"margin: 5%; font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n<h2>Behavior Technician</h2>\r\n<p><b>Job Type:</b> Part-Time / Per Diem</p><br>\r\n<strong>Job Description:</strong><br>\r\n-Build a rapport with the child.<br>\r\n-Work with child and family on the goals set forth in the behavior plan.<br>\r\n-Teach new skills.<br>\r\n-Manage behaviors, including physical and self-injurious behaviors.<br>\r\n-Observe and record progress.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Required Skills:</strong><br>\r\n-Genuine interest in working with children with autism.<br>\r\n-Ability to move/restrain clients ages 4 to 21 years old using correct safety procedures.<br>\r\n-Patience, problem-solving skills, discretion, ability to think on your feet, creativity.<br>\r\n-Ability to work well with others and be an effective part of a treatment team.<br>\r\n-Ability to work equally well independently.<br>\r\n-Strong interpersonal and writing skills.<br>\r\n-Access to reliable transportation; valid NJDL, willingness to travel.<br>\r\n-Bachelor\'s degree<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Required experience:</strong>\r\n2+ years of experience working with children on the autism spectrum.\r\n\r\n</div>\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:19:\"Behavior Technician\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:19:\"behavior-technician\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2017-10-11 18:25:25\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-10-11 18:25:25\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:54:\"http://newcarenj.org/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=333\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:10:\"post_count\";i:3;s:12:\"current_post\";i:-1;s:11:\"in_the_loop\";b:0;s:4:\"post\";r:112;s:13:\"comment_count\";i:0;s:15:\"current_comment\";i:-1;s:11:\"found_posts\";s:1:\"3\";s:13:\"max_num_pages\";d:1;s:21:\"max_num_comment_pages\";i:0;s:9:\"is_single\";b:0;s:10:\"is_preview\";b:0;s:7:\"is_page\";b:0;s:10:\"is_archive\";b:0;s:7:\"is_date\";b:0;s:7:\"is_year\";b:0;s:8:\"is_month\";b:0;s:6:\"is_day\";b:0;s:7:\"is_time\";b:0;s:9:\"is_author\";b:0;s:11:\"is_category\";b:0;s:6:\"is_tag\";b:0;s:6:\"is_tax\";b:0;s:9:\"is_search\";b:0;s:7:\"is_feed\";b:0;s:15:\"is_comment_feed\";b:0;s:12:\"is_trackback\";b:0;s:7:\"is_home\";b:1;s:6:\"is_404\";b:0;s:8:\"is_embed\";b:0;s:8:\"is_paged