(314, 1, '2017-09-17 19:37:41', '2017-09-17 19:37:41', '<div class=\"careers-container\" style=\"margin: -2.5% 0;\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://newcarenj.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/careers7.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-262 aligncenter\" src=\"http://newcarenj.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/careers7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n<div class=\"reasons-container\" style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2; padding: 20px; margin-top: -55px;\">\r\n<div class=\"apply-btn\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a role=\"button\" href=\"#jobs\">\r\n<input id=\"button-4\" style=\"background-color: #c98d24;\" name=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"View Open Positions\" />\r\n</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"career-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 5%; font-family: sans-serif; text-align: center;\">\r\n<h2>Reasons to Work for New Care Associates</h2>\r\n<h3>Challenge Yourself</h3>\r\nWorking with new people means there is never a dull moment. At New Care Associates, you will have the pleasure of working with children and parents of different backgrounds, which will open your eyes to new perspectives. The challenge is to establish trusting relationships and customize a plan that works for everyone involved.\r\n<h3>Help Improve the Lives of Others</h3>\r\nWith your help, families of children with mental health disabilities can successfully participate in their community. The resources that you will provide will ultimately make their daily living situation better.\r\n<h3>Form Connections</h3>\r\nThere is nothing more rewarding than to see clients grow and develop through our services. Clients that were once closed-off and guarded have become open and pleasantly communicative.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--reasons-container-->\r\n<div id=\"jobs\" class=\"positions\" style=\"text-align: center; color: #fff; font-weight: bold; background-color: #002266; padding: 7% 5%; margin-top: -55px; margin-bottom: -100px;\">\r\n<h2>Open Positions</h2>\r\n<a style=\"color: #fff; font-family: sans-serif;\" href=\"http://newcarenj.org/behavior-technician/\">Behavior Technician\"</a>\r\n<a style=\"color: #fff; font-family: sans-serif;\" href=\"http://newcarenj.org/licensed-clinician/\">Licensed Clinician</a>\r\n<a style=\"color: #fff; font-family: sans-serif;\" href=\"http://newcarenj.org/bcba/\">BCBA</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--positions-->\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '232-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-17 19:37:41', '2017-09-17 19:37:41', '', 232, 'http://newcarenj.org/232-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(315, 1, '2017-09-17 19:40:40', '2017-09-17 19:40:40', '<div class=\"page-margin\" margin:5%; font-family:san-serif;>\r\n<h2>Behavior Technician</h2>\r\n<strong>The Behavior Technician will:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>build a rapport with the child.</li>\r\n 	<li>work with child and family on the goals set forth in the behavior plan.</li>\r\n 	<li>teach new skills.</li>\r\n 	<li>manage behaviors, including physical and self-injurious behaviors.</li>\r\n 	<li>observe and record progress.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Required Skills:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Genuine interest in working with children with autism.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ability to move/restrain clients ages 4 to 21 years old using correct safety procedures.</li>\r\n 	<li>Patience, problem-solving skills, discretion, ability to think on your feet, creativity.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ability to work well with others and be an effective part of a treatment team.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ability to work equally well independently.</li>\r\n 	<li>Strong interpersonal and writing skills.</li>\r\n 	<li>Access to reliable transportation; valid NJDL, willingness to travel.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bachelor\'s degree .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Required experience:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>2+ years of experience working with children on the autism spectrum.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEqual Opportunity/Affirmative Action employer. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, national origin, disability, or protected Veteran status.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"apply-btn\">\r\n<a role=\"button\">\r\n<input id=\"button-5\" name=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Apply Now\" />\r\n</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Behavior Technician', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '292-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-17 19:40:40', '2017-09-17 19:40:40', '', 292, 'http://newcarenj.org/292-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
