(341, 1, '2017-09-18 15:04:11', '2017-09-18 15:04:11', '<div class=\"careers-container\" style=\"margin: -2.5% 0;\">\r\n<div class=\"career-image\">\r\n<a href=\"http://newcarenj.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/careers7.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-262 aligncenter\" src=\"http://newcarenj.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/careers7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"reasons-container\" style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2; padding: 20px; margin-top: -55px;\">\r\n<div class=\"apply-btn\" style=\"text-align: center; position: relative; left: 15px;\"><a role=\"button\" href=\"#jobs\">\r\n<input id=\"button-4\" style=\"background-color: #c98d24;\" name=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"View Open Positions\" />\r\n</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"career-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 5%; font-family: sans-serif; text-align: center;\">\r\n<h2>Reasons to Work for New Care Associates</h2>\r\n<h3>Challenge Yourself</h3>\r\nWorking with new people means there is never a dull moment. At New Care Associates, you will have the pleasure of working with children and parents of different backgrounds, which will open your eyes to new perspectives. The challenge is to establish trusting relationships and customize a plan that works for everyone involved.\r\n<h3>Help Improve the Lives of Others</h3>\r\nWith your help, families of children with mental health disabilities can successfully participate in their community. The resources that you will provide will ultimately make their daily living situation better.\r\n<h3>Form Connections</h3>\r\nThere is nothing more rewarding than to see clients grow and develop through our services. Clients that were once closed-off and guarded have become open and pleasantly communicative.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--reasons-container-->\r\n<div id=\"jobs\" class=\"positions\" style=\"text-align: center; color: #fff; font-weight: bold; background-color: #002266; padding: 7% 5%; margin-top: -55px; margin-bottom: -100