(343, 1, '2017-09-20 02:16:26', '2017-09-20 02:16:26', '<div class=\"page-margin\" style=\"margin: 5%; font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n<h2>Licensed Clinician</h2>\r\n<p><b>Job Type:</b> Part-Time / Per Diem</p><br><br>\r\nWe are currently seeking licensed clinicians (LAC/LPC, LMFTA/LMFT, and LSW/LCSW) in Northern NJ to provide home-based counseling to children and families in need of intervention.  We are particularly interested in candidates that have experience working with children with Developmental Disabilities including Autism.  Services utilize a strength-based and solution-focused intervention style. Experience utilizing positive behavior supports is a plus.\r\n\r\n<strong>Required Skills </strong>\r\n-Minimum of master\'s degree in related field\r\n-Current valid New Jersey clinical license (LAC/LPC, LMFTA/LMFT, and LSW/LCSW or Licensed Psychologist)\r\n-Valid NJ Driver\'s License and ability to travel to clients\' homes\r\n\r\n<strong>Required Experience </strong>\r\n1+ years of experience working with children with mental health and behavioral challenges.\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Licensed Clinician', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '338-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-09-20 02:16:26', '2017-09-20 02:16:26', '', 338, 'http://newcarenj.org/338-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
